{"tid":2342522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★若阿里巴巴被認定構成濫用市場支配地位，可能被責令停止違法行為，沒收違法所得！","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T08:34:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcd72930782856d87820d9aca5b2ea43fc9a50c","tid":2342522,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，有關阿里巴巴涉嫌壟斷調查全部結束。報道引述浙江省市場監管局負責人表示，國家市場監管總局調查組執法人員在上星期四，進駐阿里巴巴開展調查，對公司及部門相關負責人進行調查詢問，並提取相關證據資料，阿里巴巴積極配合，認真接受調查組詢問，及時提供相關資料，自覺接受調查，整個過程平穩有序。<br />\n<br />\n另外，浙江省市場監管局負責人表示，對阿里巴巴立案調查，並不意味國家對平台經濟鼓勵、支持的態度有所改變，反而是為了更好地規範和發展平台經濟，引導、促進其健康發展，以期為經濟高品質發展做出更大貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述專家分析，若阿里巴巴被認定構成濫用市場支配地位，按照《反壟斷法》規定，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">公司可能被責令停止違法行為，沒收違法所得</span></strong>，並以上一年度銷售額的1%至10%作為罰款。公開資料顯示，阿里巴巴對上一個財政年度的實現營收為3768億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567301-20201227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567301-20201227.htm&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=b21c5279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567301-20201227.htm&h=ce0c666c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567301-20201227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11b9facbd1af0b4863c236507249b0880c02075c","tid":2342522,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"超回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3dcfa7960d602b7255d0417dd261242a14eb22","tid":2342522,"uid":217146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"聽日會反彈？"},{"pid":"cb9502d00eeebdd380c2fc9bcbc05d6992822b29","tid":2342522,"uid":56982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvdbEFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvdbEFS.png&h=96311180&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac96e5d99c1ea54a60fa805b35f7b54e7467c596","tid":2342522,"uid":16326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"共產黨沒收企業成功回血"},{"pid":"6a805996e19e81cd7bffece92246e0ed8a91c0bd","tid":2342522,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"馬生：畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b9a142429c690f09d78244086cb8be6a0f8aa1","tid":2342522,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"個市場支現地位咪又係你班支共推上去既"},{"pid":"84c3d61c9f38d4ccf177a2454481c870d6081c11","tid":2342522,"uid":180184,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dM4ZHQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dM4ZHQ.gif&h=411e2e71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03bf2c4caeb1b423f8ed6cc711b91231bda55e17","tid":2342522,"uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"無錢咪出聲, 做咩做得咁難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}